                        <interp inst="t18470614-name-274" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN THOMAS</persName>
                  </hi>. On the 30th of May I went from Hungerford-mar<lb></lb>ket to London-bridge—a man asked me if I had lost my handkerchief—I said I had—he turned me back, and took the prisoner—I have not had my handkerchief again—I had it safe before.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18470614-name-275" type="witnessName">
